subject: Tennis
French Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Wawrinka, the eighth-seeded Swiss player, advanced to his first final at Roland Garros with a 6-3, 6-7 (1), 7-6 (3), 6-4 win over France’s Tsonga.
